Happy to see Astro Lan II (minted a year ago) picked up by @iki-jima

Improvised pattern-writing 'procedurally' typed on an Olivetti Lettera 22  mechanical typewriter.

There are always a few (physical) pieces available in this object collection. I try to keep it topped up with my favourite outputs. I guess I may have up to 400 typewriter drawings completed now - ready for that retrospective üòÜ üôè
